# Inbox scan (consumers only — omit for producers)

Run `ls {{PROJECT_ROOT}}/.orchestrator/tasks/inbox/` and read every frontmatter.
Filter by `consumer_role: {{CONSUMER_ROLE}}` and `area: {{AREAS}}`. Honour `blocked_by`.

Pickup protocol (full version: see Escape hatches below):
1. `mv` from `inbox/` to `in-progress/`.
2. Stamp `## Activity` (branch + ISO start).
3. Do the work.
4. Re-run the test that originally caught the issue.
5. Append `## Resolution`, `mv` to `done/`.
6. Or append `## Escalation reason`, `mv` to `escalated/`.

